    Dispatches Ontick and render events to GameObjects All GameObjects should subscribe to gameObjects list Will be instanced in Map class

    Adds functionalities to ImprovedSprite that are specific to GameObjects Implements GameObject to add generic implementations for GameObject methods

    Projectiles always have a target student that they move towards Handles checking if it hit target and calls the tower the projectile came from, to handle adding participation to the student
